    "comment": "Rationale: Super-resolution STED imaging performed in rat hippocampal neurons revealed localization of MAP1BLC3 at the presynaptic boutons labeled by Synaptophysin.. Experimental description: This antibody was purified from hybridoma (clone 4E12) supernatant using protein A agarose. This hybridoma was established by fusion of mouse myeloma cell P3U1 with C3H mouse lymphocyte immunized with the recombinant human LC3 [MAP1LC3B (1-120 aa)].\nThis antibody reacts with LC3 (MAP1LC3A, B) on Immunocytochemistry, Western blotting and Immunoprecipitation.",
